OL,3,CVisually impaired mum told she 'should
OL,4,Cnot have kids' in disability hate crime
OL,6,FITV News' Ned Kelly spoke to Samantha
OL,7,Fand Rachel about the discrimination
OL,8,Fthey have faced as disabled parents.
OL,10,FA mother with a disability says she
OL,11,Fhas been told she "shouldn't be having
OL,12,Fa kid" while travelling home on the
OL,13,Fbus from a soft play area with her son.
OL,15,FSamantha Ralfe, and her husband Martin
OL,16,FRalfe live in St Helens, both living
OL,17,Fwith a visual impairment.
