OL,3,CVisually impaired mum told she 'should
OL,4,Cnot have kids' in disability hate crime
OL,6,FThe couple raise awareness on TikTok
OL,7,Fabout having a disability while
OL,8,Fbringing up their three-year-old boy
OL,9,FLeo.
OL,11,FSam says she often experiences hate
OL,12,Fonline and abuse in public, she said:
OL,13,F"Myself and Leo, and Bailey, my guide
OL,14,Fdog, were on the bus just coming home
OL,15,Ffrom a soft play... and I could hear
OL,16,Fsome woman behind saying that 'oh look
OL,17,Fshe's disabled, she shouldn't be
OL,18,Fhaving a kid'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
