OL,3,CVisually impaired mum told she 'should
OL,4,Cnot have kids' in disability hate crime
OL,6,FShe said: "In the moment once your
OL,7,Fbusy looking after your child and your
OL,8,Fguide dog, you just kind of let it go
OL,9,Fover your head, you don't really care.
OL,11,F"But it's when your sat at home just
OL,12,Fbefore you go to sleep, you sit there
OL,13,Fand think about the day and it does
OL,14,Fget to you.
OL,16,F"Later on you do think, are they
OL,17,Fright? Am I the one in the wrong? Am I
OL,18,Fthe bad person for doing this? But you
OL,19,Fjust have to let it go the best you
OL,20,Fcan."
