OL,3,CVisually impaired mum told she 'should
OL,4,Cnot have kids' in disability hate crime
OL,6,FDisability hate crime is defined as
OL,7,Fdiscrimination motivated by a person's
OL,8,Fdisability.
OL,10,FIn just one year more than 13,000
OL,11,Freports of disability hate crime were
OL,12,Fmade, but only around 1% resulted in a
OL,13,Fcriminal charge, according to
OL,14,Fgovernment statistics across England
OL,15,Fand Wales in 2022-2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
