OL,3,CVisually impaired mum told she 'should
OL,4,Cnot have kids' in disability hate crime
OL,6,FShe believes people do not pair
OL,7,Fdisability and parenting together.
OL,9,F"When she was very little I think that
OL,10,Fwas the hardest bit," she said.
OL,12,F"She ran off on me once in the
OL,13,FTrafford Centre, oh it was a
OL,14,Fnightmare, because I can't chase her,
OL,15,FI can't bring her back.
OL,17,F"Somebody came up to me and said
OL,18,F'well, if you can't chase after your
OL,19,Fchild then you really shouldn't have
OL,20,Fher here.'
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
