OL,6,F"Comments like that sometimes makes
OL,7,Fyou question yourself, but it also
OL,8,Fmakes you question yourself when your
OL,9,Fkid runs off and you know you can't
OL,10,Fgrab them, that kind of sows a seed of
OL,11,Fdoubt in your head."
OL,13,F"Hate crimes against disabled people
OL,14,Fare despicable and we encourage people
OL,15,Fto report incidents to the police.
OL,17,FA Crown Prosecution Service
OL,18,Fspokesperson said: "Hate crimes
OL,19,Fagainst disabled people are despicable
OL,20,Fand we encourage people to report
OL,21,Fincidents to the police.
